Package org.microbean.type

Class AbstractType

java.lang.Object
org.microbean.type.AbstractType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Type
Direct Known Subclasses:
DefaultGenericArrayType, DefaultParameterizedType, LowerBoundedWildcardType, PartiallyImplementedTypeVariable, UnboundedWildcardType, UpperBoundedWildcardType
public abstract class AbstractType
extends Object
implements Serializable, Type
A common abstract superclass for Type implementations.

All AbstractType implementations must be at least lossily serializable.

Author:
Laird Nelson
